#: holidaycategories.cpp:77
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Public Holiday: a day-off from work or school (typically) to commemorate a "
"historical event, or to honor people.  Public holidays are always bounded to "
"a political region at national, regional or local level."
msgstr ""
"Die feriate public: un die libere de travalio o schola (typicamente) pro "
"commemorar  un evento historic, o pro honorar personas. Le dies feriate "
"public es sempre ligate  a un region politic a nivello national, regional o "
"local."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:82
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Civil Service Holiday: a day-off from work for government workers but not a "
"day off for private sector workers."
msgstr ""
"Die feriate del servicio civil: un die libere de labor pro le empleatos "
"public, sed  non un die libere pro le travaliatores del sector private."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:85
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Religious Holiday: a special day in a religion and not bound to any "
"political region. Religions can have holidays that range in devotion to "
"those were work/school are forbidden, days of prayer obligation, to "
"historical remembrances, etc. Governments often have public holidays for "
"some religious holidays."
msgstr ""
"Die feriate religiose: un die special in un religion e non ligate a alcun "
"region politic. Le religiones pote haber dies feriate que varia in devotion "
"de illos ubi  le travalio o le schola es prohibite, dies de obligation de "
"precaria, a rememorantias historic, etc. Le governos frequentemente ha dies "
"feriate  public pro alcun dies feriate religiose."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:91
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"School Holiday: a day-off from school, either as a one-off Public Holiday or "
"extended periods between school terms.  This can vary widely depending on "
"school level, type, location."
msgstr ""
"Vacantia scholar: un die libere de schola, sia como un die feriate public "
"isolate  o periodos extendite inter le terminos scholar. Isto pote variar "
"amplemente  dependente del nivello, typo, e location del schola."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:96
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Government Holiday: a special day recognized by a political region but "
"without a day-off for workers, students, etc."
msgstr ""
"Feria governamental: un die special recognoscite per un region politic sed "
"sin un die libere pro travaliatores, studentes, etc."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:99
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid "Financial Holiday: banks and markets may close on some public holidays"
msgstr ""
"Feria financiari: le bancos e mercatos pote clauder in certe dies ferial "
"public."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:102
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Cultural Holiday: a special day in the culture and therefore usually bound "
"to a political region. A day where people celebrate in some fashion. eg. "
"Halloween, St. Valentines"
msgstr ""
"Feria cultural: un die special in le cultura e per lo tanto usualmente "
"ligate a un region politic. Un die in que le gente celebra de alcun "
"maniera.  p.ex. Halloween, San Valentin."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:107
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Commemorative Holiday: a special day to remember usually bound to a "
"political region. Not a day-off from work or school; banks are open, etc."
msgstr ""
"Die commemorative: un die special pro rememorar, habitualmente ligate a un "
"region politic. Non un die libere de travalio o schola; le bancas  es "
"aperite, etc."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:111
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Historical Holiday: similar to a Commemorative Holiday but historical in "
"nature."
msgstr ""
"Feria historic: simile a un feria commemorative sed de natura historic."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:114
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Name Day Holiday: in some political regions each day is assigned a first "
"name and persons with that name celebrate that day as their \"Name Day\"."
msgstr ""
"Festa del Die de Nomine: in alcun regiones politic cata die es assignate un "
"prenomine e personas con ille nomine celebra ille die como lor  \"Die de "
"Nomine\"."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:119
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Seasonal Days: the day corresponds to a seasonal event like an equinox, "
"solstice, daylight saving time starts/ends."
msgstr ""
"Dies seasonal: le die corresponde a un evento seasonal como un equinoxio, "
"solstitio, o le initio/fin del hora de estate."

